OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright spells possible at
OL,6,Ffirst, but soon clouding over with
OL,7,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, these
OL,8,Fturning heavy in places in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. A little less warm than
OL,10,FFriday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will remain cloudy through
OL,13,Fthe evening and overnight with some
OL,14,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, heavy at
OL,15,Ffirst, gradually easing overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FDull, cool and cloudy through
OL,18,Fthe morning with a few light showers.
OL,19,FSome brighter spells may develop later
OL,20,Fin the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
